Global Steel Production Use Electric Arc Furnace Market Insights
Steel Production Use Electric Arc Furnace Market size was valued at USD 55 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 78 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Steel Production Use Electric Arc Furnace Market Overview
The global Electric Arc Furnace (EAF) market was valued at approximately $800 million in 2022 and is projected to reach $1.3 billion by 2031, reflecting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.7% from 2023 to 2031. This growth is driven by the increasing adoption of EAFs in steel production, offering advantages such as energy efficiency, reduced carbon emissions, and the ability to utilize recycled materials. The shift towards sustainable manufacturing practices and the demand for high-quality steel products are key factors contributing to the market's expansion.

